author = "Sachin Atre and Sona Deshmukh and Manjusha Kulkarni",
abstract = "Aim
To conduct a systematic and critical review of published studies on prevalence of Type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM) in urban and rural areas of India.
Methods
