Results
Of 1751 articles screened by titles and abstracts, 37 fulfilled our inclusion criteria. Majority (28 of 37; 76%) of studies were from South India, especially from the states of Tamil Nadu, Andhra Pradesh, Kerala and Karnataka. The prevalence of T2DM showed a wide range from 1.9% to 25.2%. Only 11 studies covering 24 regions separately reported the data by urban or rural location. Albeit inconsistent, 17 studies reported prevalence of T2DM by age group.
