abstract = "C1q/TNF-related protein-3 (CTRP3) is a novel adipokine with anti-inflammatory and a multitude of biological effects on glucose and lipid metabolism however, the influence of CTRP3 on incidence of diabetes mellitus remain unclear. This study investigated the effects of CTRP3 levels in obese and normal body weight young adults on insulin resistance and occurrence of diabetes mellitus.
